### README>>>>

1. Clone the repository:
   -open your terminal
   -git clone https://github.com/Naoldaba/ArtistryNexus.git
   -cd backend

2. Install Dependencies
    -npm install

3. Setup environmental variables
    -create .env file
    -add the following environment-specific variables on new lines in the form of NAME=VALUE
          -PORT = 5050
          -SECRET_KEY = bombastic sideeye
          -CONNECTION_URL = mongodb://0.0.0.0:27017/ArtistryNexus
          -GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID = //from google console
          -GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET = //from google console
          -SESSION_KEY = //anything
          -EMAIL = //host email to send OTP 
          -PASSWORD =  // App password for the above email      

4. Running the app
    -npm start

5. I generated API documentation using swagger, it can be accessed at:
    -http://localhost:5050/api-docs
